{"title":"光纤通信","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1955","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>农民John 想要用光纤连通他的N (1 &lt;= N &lt;= 1,000)个牲口棚(编号1..N)。但是，牲口棚位于一个大池塘边,他仅可以连通相邻的牲口棚。John不需要连通所有的牲口棚, 因为只有某些奶牛之间想要彼此通讯。在保证这些奶牛通讯的情况下，他想使用最少的光纤完成通信网构件工作。给出想要通讯的成对奶牛的清单，要求求出最少需使用多少根光纤。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">1</span><span style=\"\">行</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">: 2</span><span style=\"\">个整数</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">, n </span><span style=\"\">和 </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">p (</span><span style=\"\">想要通讯的奶牛对数</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">, 1&lt;=p&lt;=</span>10,000)</p>\n<p>第<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">2..p+1</span><span style=\"\">行</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">: 2</span><span style=\"\">个整数，描述想要通讯的两只奶牛的编号</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p16\">仅<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">行，即最少使用光纤数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5 2</p>\n<p>1 3</p>\n<p>4 5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>样例方案：连接<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">1-</span>2,<span style=\"\">连接</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">2-</span>3, <span style=\"\">连接</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">4-</span>5</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}